WEBVTT

00:02:26.704 --> 00:02:30.965
and wrapped rubber bands
around a watermelon until it exploded.

00:02:30.989 --> 00:02:32.570
(Laughter)

00:02:32.889 --> 00:02:36.261
Eight hundred thousand people watched

00:02:36.285 --> 00:02:40.316
the 690th rubber band
explode the watermelon,

00:02:40.340 --> 00:02:43.793
marking it as the biggest
Facebook Live event to date.

00:02:44.483 --> 00:02:47.093
The question I get most frequently is:

00:02:47.117 --> 00:02:48.950
How do you make something go viral?

00:02:49.713 --> 00:02:51.919
The question itself is misplaced;

00:02:51.943 --> 00:02:53.636
it's not about the something.

00:02:53.660 --> 00:02:56.957
It's about what the people
doing the something,

00:02:56.981 --> 00:02:58.184
reading or watching --

00:02:58.208 --> 00:02:59.488
what are they thinking?

